Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:06.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:19.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:23.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:31.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:37.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:44.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:54.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:02.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:08.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:11.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:19.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:25.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:55.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:14.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see that your hair's\Nas messy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all together again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all been acting weird\Nsince summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since you all took that\Nvacation at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,your buddy-buddy level has\Nincreased even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:09.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! Tell me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Tell me!\N- Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you're leaving me\Nout of something big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally begun!\NI'm being left out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much. Now that you understand,\Ngo over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell that he's just teasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid blue skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning, Hime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, an impressive retort...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a retort!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you that it's a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already autumn\Nand you're still in heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ichigo, how's your paper going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The assignment you were given\Nwhile you were all on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about it, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if\Nyou don't finish it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine. Anyway, things will get\Ntroublesome afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if you take too many breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PROTECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this charm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,KUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I forgot to return this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PROTECTION\N	Anyway, I don't even know\N	why I still have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm giving it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you sewing it\Nonto my uniform?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what my stupid pop did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that without even asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:05.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else besides your father\Nwould do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's not what\NI was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asking about that skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? This is... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Re- No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki... You can see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:26.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the teacher's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get to your seats, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:40.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Everyone's all here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshima and Sorimachi are never here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're delinquents, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I have\Na wonderful announcement for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'm going to introduce you\Nto a transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a stronger tool than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:01.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous for someone other\Nthan a Soul Reaper to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it has\Na visual barrier built into it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep normal humans from seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the case? Or is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...No...My stomach hurts a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who screams out loud when\Nthey have a stomach ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NHey! Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The restroom? Oh come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sado! And Inoue too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are supposed to\Nhold in stuff like that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,until they start getting\Na stomach ache!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:00.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! And I've got to pee real bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher! I also have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, Asano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's favoritism!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're favoring Ichigo\Nand the others! Favoritism!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Favoritism! Favoritism!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop it already, Keigo...\N- Favoritism! Favoritism! Favoritism!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Favoritism! Favoritism! Favoritism!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare, rare, rare!\NRare, rare, rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still Hollows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Hollows will\Nprobably continue to exist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as there are humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef or pork? Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Medium?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:15.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it all right for me to\Ntake out the usual Hollows by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to cut\Nclass as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:18.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've always wanted\Nto try cutting class
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by pretending to go\Nto the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that you're not\Nmaking any excuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's way too honest, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\NIshida didn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have\Nany spiritual power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been two weeks\Nsince we've come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry...\NHe'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He fought pretty hard even\Nwithout his power returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe in Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...Kurosaki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:13.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys actually had\Nthings to unpack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:32.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I did. I received a number\Nof parting gifts from Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she didn't just\Npush useless garbage on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude, Lirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what delicious tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, seems you've been making\Nyourself quite comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,inside that stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get used to it, this is easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two change as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:57.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,True... We'll be freeloading here at\NUrahara's Shop from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't take up too much space\Nand cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to live with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Bount sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Bounts are gone,\Nour role is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:15.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Ichigo and the others are\Nat school throughout the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much of a bother to live\Nin secret during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to just live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see everyone at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why are you asking the obvious?!\N- That hurts! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mod souls that the boss created.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:38.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They should help out around\Nhere from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now, now...\N- I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- So why don't we just get along...?\N- I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Shut up, shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:52.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KARAKURA HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The transfer student I was talking\Nabout this morning has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Introduce yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:56.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shin" from "genuine sadist" with\N"Ko" from "karashi mentaiko"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:12:00.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Hira" from "lecherous" with\N"Ko" from "Ono no Imoko" makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,OKARIH IJNIHS\N	Shinji Hirako! Pleased to meet you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako, Hirako, it's the other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at writing things backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:18.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it!\Nell, you'll be sitting... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:21.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Teacher...\NI'd like to sit next to a cute girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A cute girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,-I thought\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- you'd recover immediately...\N- Then sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- But I guess your powers\N- That's not what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- won't come back so easily.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah.\N- All right! Then sit behind there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're my neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:44.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends...Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:55.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PHYSICIAN - PEDIATRICS\NKUROSAKI CLINIC\N	  \N	No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live like this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go outside--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get friendly with busty girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:08.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop making a fuss!\NYuzu and the others will hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not make a fuss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to keep me locked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to file a suit against you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for infringement of stuffed animal rights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take everything you've got,\Neven the fuzz off your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...I want to go into your body.\NIt's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:27.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go peeping or flip skirts,\Nit'll only ruin your reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've been engaging\Nin those illegal acts all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:41.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so easy to be locked away\Nwhen sister was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:45.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sister, come back!\N- You're being a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollow! Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, again?\N- Hollow! Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well... I'll stick you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care until I come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a ruckus! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... It's been a while since\NI've been in his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go out to do a little\Nof this and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressing up like a Soul Reaper\Nand acting so suspicious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Zennosuke Kurumadani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rukia Kuchiki was\Ndragged away for some crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was placed in charge of\Nthis area instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an elite Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ichigo Kurosaki!\NI'm a Substitute Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my combat pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A combat pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:24.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen or heard\Nof such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this thing?\NIt isn't any help at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to apologize,\Nnow's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...a zanpakuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:07.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make too much noise,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys with Spiritual Pressure like\Nyou shouldn't make such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will tremble\Nand they'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll notice? Who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:28.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Must I tell you everything\Nbefore you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that noise? It scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Ichigo found me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's night, but it's the first time\NI've been outside in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enjoy my brief,\Nyouthful escapades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything illegal, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be good and\Nkeep my promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:20.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:27.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It got here by ripping\Na hole through space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a Menos Grande?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's getting in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:53.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've forgotten me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Fisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}URAHARA'S SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:31.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:36.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako... Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you were\Nreleasing your Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asking you who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really that concerned\Nwith who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:53.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow mask--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:16.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...\NA zanpakuto and a Hollow mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:25.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Soul Reaper who's stepped\Ninto the domain of the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:30.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you..."Let's be friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:39.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us...Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:52.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible\NSpiritual Pressure he has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really a Menos Grande?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with what remains of\Nmy Spiritual Energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a way to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renze Forumeru Venti Gral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Haizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were Ginto that I charged\Nwith Spirit Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,during the battle in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not be enough to defeat him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll help me put up a fight\Nat the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant Regeneration!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His upper body disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:57.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He split?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Were there two of them\Nfrom the beginning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Addressing your father by his name\Nwithout any sign of respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as always,\Naren't you, Uryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:07.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:13.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:18.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:23.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:29.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:34.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:46.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:52.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:57.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:03.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:11.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that Ishida's father\Nwas a Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that his father\Nhas those clothes as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:29.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Those clothes are\Nthe traditional Quincy attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your father are both Quincies?\NThat's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say that you're any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N- Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on\Nin this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:41.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all sorts of weird folks\Nall gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:43.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are humans who can see me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a Substitute Soul Reaper\Nshows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:47.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:51.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the disruption in Seireitei,\Nwe got behind on informing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You got behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:55.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumadani, please continue to\Ndestroy petty Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:56.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Petty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:59.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But try not to interfere with\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:00.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I one of the elite?